data.description: Discover the serenity of 530 Clipper Creek Rd. in Auburn, CA! Nestled on a private dead-end road, this 3-bed, 2-bath manufactured home on a permanent foundation offers breathtaking views and tranquility just minutes from Auburn. Situated on 4.6 acres, the property features outbuildings for storage and RV pads. Enjoy the updated kitchen and flooring, or unleash your creativity with personalized updates. Whether you prefer the charm of its current state or envision a bespoke transformation, this property invites you to embrace the beauty of nature with the convenience of proximity. Your dream home awaits!
